{"tid":2117389,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真係好掛住香港","createTime":"2020-07-20T22:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T07:30:49.000Z","uid":247527,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"636909c759da45ad2577a167d44283d67c1450ac","tid":2117389,"uid":247527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T22:17:33.000Z","msg":"由反修例開始引發既一切，香港好似變得物是人非咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由反修例示威開始，演變為對軍權同極權政府以及共產黨政治恐怖統治既垂死反抗<br />\n<br />\n昔日沉積落嚟既影響同隱憂一次過同你挖晒出嚟浮晒面，就好似沉喺水底既沙咁<br />\n<br />\n香港已經唔可以再好似以前粉飾太平既時候，用無奈嚟回應好多既走盞同灰色地帶，香港人選擇用抗爭嚟追求公正及自由既社會，抵抗當權者執法者既濫權同越權甚至干犯罪行，用毅力與血去維繫法治社會既完整<br />\n<br />\n而年頭至今爆發既武漢肺炎就好似為氣氛灰暗既香港再添多一層黑灰色既filter咁，連出街都戴住口罩，驚做錯做漏衛生，驚病毒散播，驚身上痴到病毒，驚口罩保護唔夠好。喺呢段時期諗得負面啲簡直就好似係白色恐怖咁，只要行錯一步就會踏入死亡<br />\n<br />\n真係好掛住以前既香港，喺街度食冷面食燒賣飲奶茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，出街聞到口罩同呼氣以外既味道，返工唔使驚住俾人炒魷然後搵十世都搵唔到工，唔使擔心狗狗出街會感染肺炎，可以約班frd落bar同幫襯好好食既黃店，想做乜就做乜既生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n宜家香港經歷緊既可能係蛻變既過程，可能只係融解前既沫渣<br />\n<br />\n我真係好撚中意香港<br />\n然而正常既香港喺土共眼中則係無理取鬧<br />\n721，唔好忘記由港共魔爪撕開既警隊醜陋原貌<br />\n同埋呢個政權同軍權所欠香港既債<br />\n------------------------------------<br />\n鏗鏘集：7.21 誰主真相<br />\n<br />\n7.21發生近一年，事件論述由最初的白衣人襲擊市民；演變成係白衣人與黑衣人的暴力衝突。鏗鏘集再次翻查當日閉路電視、網絡片段裡的線索，追查當中的人物，了解他們口中的事件真相<br />\n<br />\n【 721 誰主真相：警察篇】<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hongkong_info/2625\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhongkong_info%2F2625&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhPzX0Nqj3uEASyejP0bzfnYY%3D&h=3206e301\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hongkong_info/2625</a><br />\n【 721 誰主真相：遇襲者篇】<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hongkong_info/2624\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhongkong_info%2F2624&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhPzX0Nqj3uEASyejP0bzfnYY%3D&h=bd5ecc12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hongkong_info/2624</a><br />\n【 721 誰主真相：厦溪白衣人篇】<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hongkong_info/2630\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhongkong_info%2F2630&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhPzX0Nqj3uEASyejP0bzfnYY%3D&h=699c636c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hongkong_info/2630</a><br />\n【 721 誰主真相：搵人篇】<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hongkong_info/2659\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhongkong_info%2F2659&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhPzX0Nqj3uEASyejP0bzfnYY%3D&h=e96779c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hongkong_info/2659</a><br />\n【 721 誰主真相：何君堯篇】<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hongkong_info/2660\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhongkong_info%2F2660&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhPzX0Nqj3uEASyejP0bzfnYY%3D&h=90fa179a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hongkong_info/2660</a><br />\n<br />\n全集重溫 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=or4B7NpHwbY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dor4B7NpHwbY&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhPzX0Nqj3uEASyejP0bzfnYY%3D&h=099ffb6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=or4B7NpHwbY</a>"},{"pid":"e7d957ccc89c652a02a7bdbb7b90972243917995","tid":2117389,"uid":247527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T22:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好想瘋狂飲奶綠瘋狂食肚痾冷面"},{"pid":"56d26ba59216ae6c2c79887814cf42fbe84656ee","tid":2117389,"uid":247527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T22:40:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可摸耳俾返香港我"},{"pid":"ce756e9fae27824557